# Verifolio Core Rules

Read `AGENTS.md` before working.

The most catastrophic rules, inline:

- Do not modify locked document versions.
- Do not expose S3/MinIO URLs publicly.
- Do not bypass domain authorization.
- Do not move regional data (including consent records) out of its region or send it to non-regional providers.

The full non-negotiable list lives in `AGENTS.md` § Non-Negotiable Rules — read it before any change. `AGENTS.md` is the single canonical rule source.
